  m_text: 'Now you know how to move, let''s learn some advanced controls!


    1)
    Hold your left wrist in front of you to view your control panel


    You interact
    with this using your laser and the button on your right controller, just like
    clicking the buttons so far.


    3) Try setting one of the sliders to a new
    value by holding and releasing the trigger.'
