  m_text: 'Can you see how the Earth is tilted? This is what causes the seasons!

    When
    the Earth''s axis points towards the Sun, it is summer for that hemisphere. When
    the Earth''s axis points away the sun, it is winter for that hemisphere.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
