  m_text: "Mars has been given the nickname the \"Red Planet\u201D because of its
    red appearance, caused by iron oxide dust covering its surface. Mars is the furthest
    rocky planet from the Sun and is home to some huge extinct volcanoes. We have
    sent many rovers to Mars to study its surface, such as NASA's Curiosity Rover."
