  m_text: 'Awesome! Now let''s learn how to move!


    1) Push the joystick on your
    left controller forwards to travel towards this sign


    2) Now push the joystick
    back to travel back!


    Notice how your laser appears when you rest your thumb
    on the joystick?


    3) Point your laser in the air and push the joystick forward
    and backward to travel up and down.'
